{"tid":1629593,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾位手足捐出電話，有需要既義士可以聯絡我","createTime":"2019-10-06T09:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T10:25:37.000Z","uid":320119,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"328f48c909c8049e72b6c142a352ed439af3833f","tid":1629593,"uid":320119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:55:14.000Z","msg":"我p牌推唔到舊post，唔知我係邊個既巴絲可以睇番：<br />\n專門整iPhone壞主板之你問我答（義士免費整iPhone)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1559974\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1559974</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫一位義士整好既iPhone 7plus (免費幫各位義士整iPhone)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1588916\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1588916</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本來我只係幫各位免費整iphone <br />\n有幾位手足主動搵我，佢地捐出電話叫我比有需要既義士<br />\n雖然都係舊款電話，但功能完全無問題，價值唔高最岩各位義士隨時可以成部電話掉落水<br />\n<br />\n有需要既手足可以聯絡我，唔洗唔好意思，係大家既一番心意，我只係幫手轉送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，同大家分享一部幫位絲打整好既6s入水唔著機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Joy22Jz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJoy22Jz.jpg&h=3c7c89a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一打開部機，已經見到有螺絲生銹，證明已經入左水一段時間<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LYgsuoX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLYgsuoX.jpg&h=9e9eb632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔著機既電話首先睇下電流<br />\n一扣電就大電流，說明開機電路上面有嚴重短路，而且係保護管擋住既一個電流<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m13B7bm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm13B7bm.jpg&h=eab1bed3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoyKwC6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoyKwC6.jpg&h=dbf58be2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h6cn2K3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh6cn2K3.jpg&h=2b4b8fb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n試水紙已經變紅，呢部機主要係頂部入水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jiZE4Y8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjiZE4Y8.jpg&h=1aa0abbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n比大家睇下保護管既實際大小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為保護管係前面擋住所有大電流<br />\n所以要搵出真正短路既地方就要拆左保護管<br />\n再短接保護管焊點，再加電<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uxFEkyi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuxFEkyi.jpg&h=1967503d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以上係顯微鏡既世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加錫將4個焊點短接<br />\n再加電，就會搵到真正短路既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CauNux2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCauNux2.jpg&h=1f27da35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n松香法搵出真正短路既電容，換左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emVADrA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemVADrA.jpg&h=7cac5885&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n粒電容已經燒到黃左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ingTp6Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FingTp6Q.jpg&h=2563f6e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成功開機了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整機既巴絲可以ig或tg聯絡我，<span style=\"color: red;\">一律免費</span><br />\nIg: iPhonemotherboardhk <br />\nTg:<a h